                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9742" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1465</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">658 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">融资转型添活力，邮储定增绘新篇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financing Transformation Adds Vitality, Postal Savings Bank of China Opens a New Chapter with Fixed Increase</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">任莉莉，徐丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕山大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国邮政储蓄银行</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">定向增发；国有企业；融资；战略转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Private Placement; State-owned Enterprises; Financing; Strategic Transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着国有企业股权改革的持续推进，是否以及如何吸纳更多投资者加入国有企业，帮助国有企业缓解融资压力、助力国有企业发展已成为当前政府与企业共同关注的焦点。针对性强、效率高、直接面向特定投资者筹集资金并优化股权结构的定向增发受到了许多上市公司的青睐。中国邮政储蓄银行是一家全国性的零售商业银行，在银行业竞争日益加剧的情况下，面临着补充核心资本与业务转型的双重困境。本案例以2023年中国邮政储蓄银行定向增发事件为主体，向学生展示邮储银行在定增过程中遇到的问题和解决方法，与定增后业务转型的发展历程。本案例旨在引导学生深入了解定向增发过程中的运作机制，掌握定向增发在企业融资和战略转型中的作用，培养学生形成正确的价值观和全局观，也为其他银行的融资转型发展提供借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the continuous advancement of state-owned enterprise equity reform, whether and how to attract more investors to join state-owned enterprises, help state-owned enterprises alleviate financing pressure and promote the development of state-owned enterprises has become the focus of common concern of the current government and enterprises. The targeted issuance of shares, which is highly targeted, efficient, directly targeting specific investors to raise funds and optimize the equity structure, has been favored by many listed companies. China Postal Savings Bank is a national retail commercial bank. In the context of increasingly fierce competition in the banking industry, it faces the dual dilemma of supplementing core capital and business transformation. This case takes the targeted issuance of China Postal Savings Bank in 2023 as the main event, showing students the problems and solutions encountered by Postal Savings Bank in the process of targeted issuance, and the development process of business transformation after the targeted issuance. This case aims to guide students to have a deep understanding of the operating mechanism of the targeted issuance process, grasp the role of targeted issuance in corporate financing and strategic transformation, cultivate students to form correct values and overall perspectives, and also provide reference significance for the financing transformation and development of other banks.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理理论与实务</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">优序融资理论；定向增发概念；融资动机；融资目标与对象匹配原则；战略投资者；市场流动性风险；信息不对称；协同效应；平衡管理理论；核心竞争力理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-08</td>
                            </tr>
